Who would you book the next Christmas evening with here?🎅🏻

Nestled in mountain ranges and perched at 1616m above sea level, Dolomitenhütte offers you a quiet sanctuary away from the hustle of everyday life. It boasts unparalleled views of the Dolomites and its surrounding meadows and valleys!

The chalet’s unique and cozy ambiance will make you feel like you’ve stepped into a different world. Explore the surrounding forests or spend an afternoon walk at a nearby lake.

Video by: @piet_flosse 
Model: @xniiiiina 
Location: @dolomitenhuette_lienz 
#mountainadventures

Wich of these places by @oyehaug from Norway would you rather visit? Let us know in the comments!
